6.7, 705.9, 1055.4, 730.8]}, {"text": "Amortization of Acquisition-related Intangible Assets", "bbox": [110.9, 732.4, 610.5, 757.4]}, {"text": "(647.9)", "bbox": [798.3, 732.4, 888.4, 757.4]}, {"text": "(554.7)", "bbox": [965.3, 732.4, 1055.4, 757.4]}, {"text": "Consolidated Operating Income", "bbox": [110.9, 783.9, 409.3, 808.9]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [739.5, 783.9, 756.6, 808.9]}, {"text": "1,245.2", "bbox": [790.6, 783.9, 888.4, 808.9]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [906.6, 783.9, 923.6, 808.9]}, {"text": "1,206.0", "bbox": [957.6, 783.9, 1055.4, 808.9]}, {"text": "3%", "bbox": [1145.1, 783.9, 1181.3, 808.9]}, {"text": "Reportable Segments Operating Income Margin", "bbox": [81.4, 837.0, 527.3, 861.9]}, {"text": "18.1%", "bbox": [811.6, 837.0, 888.4, 861.9]}, {"text": "17.4%", "bbox": [978.6, 837.0, 1055.4, 861.9]}, {"text": "Consolidated Operating Income Margin", "bbox": [81.4, 890.0, 452.9, 914.9]}, {"text": "10.6%", "bbox": [811.6, 890.0, 888.4, 914.9]}, {"text": "11.4%", "bbox": [978.6, 890.0, 1055.4, 914.9]}, {"text": "Income from the company’s reportable segments increased 16% to $2.13 billion in 2011 due primarily to profit", "bbox": [138.4, 943.0, 1164.1, 967.9]}, {"text": "on incremental sales from acquisitions and, to a lesser extent, existing businesses as well as from productivity", "bbox": [81.4, 969.5, 1092.0, 994.4]}, {"text": "improvements.", "bbox": [81.4, 995.5, 223.8, 1020.4]}, {"text": "Analytical Technologies", "bbox": [81.4, 1047.0, 326.3, 1071.9]}, {"text": "(Dollars in millions)", "bbox": [81.4, 1098.5, 274.1, 1123.4]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [789.4, 1098.5, 858.4, 1123.4]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [957.0, 1098.5, 1025.9, 1123.4]}, {"text": "Change", "bbox": [1105.5, 1098.5, 1181.2, 1123.4]}, {"text": "Revenues", "bbox": [81.4, 1150.0, 176.1, 1174.9]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [709.5, 1150.0, 726.6, 1174.9]}, {"text": "3,845.4", "bbox": [761.1, 1150.0, 858.4, 1174.9]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [877.0, 1150.0, 894.1, 1174.9]}, {"text": "3,238.2", "bbox": [928.1, 1150.0, 1025.9, 1174.9]}, {"text": "19%", "bbox": [1133.4, 1150.0, 1181.0, 1174.9]}, {"text": "Operating Income Margin", "bbox": [81.4, 1201.5, 326.2, 1226.4]}, {"text": "18.7%", "bbox": [782.1, 1201.5, 858.4, 1226.4]}, {"text": "17.0%", "bbox": [949.1, 1201.5, 1025.9, 1226.4]}, {"text": "1.7", "bbox": [1135.3, 1201.5, 1181.0, 1226.4]}, {"text": "Sales in the Analytical Technologies segment increased $607 million to $3.85 billion in 2011. The increase was", "bbox": [138.4, 1259.0, 1167.8, 1283.9]}, {"text": "due to acquisitions, including Dionex, higher revenue at existing businesses and, to a lesser extent, the favorable", "bbox": [81.4, 1285.5, 1116.4, 1310.4]}, {"text": "effects of currency translation. Had Dionex and the company been combined from the beginning of 2010, pro forma", "bbox": [81.4, 1312.0, 1151.2, 1337.0]}, {"text": "revenues would have increased $349 million (10%) over pro forma 2010 revenues, including increases of $47 million", "bbox": [81.4, 1338.1, 1165.3, 1363.0]}, {"text": "due to other acquisitions, $95 million due to the favorable effects of currency translation and $207 million (6%) due to", "bbox": [81.4, 1364.6, 1173.6, 1389.5]}, {"text": "higher revenues at existing businesses. The increase in pro forma revenue at existing businesses was primarily due to", "bbox": [81.4, 1391.1, 1159.9, 1416.0]}, {"text": "increased demand. Demand was particularly strong for instruments serving industrial and applied markets. The", "bbox": [81.4, 1417.1, 1104.7, 1442.0]}, {"text": "increase in revenues was offset in part by lower stimulus-funded sales in Japan in the first quarter of 2011 which", "bbox": [81.4, 1443.6, 1118.7, 1468.5]}, {"text": "decreased pro forma growth by 1 percentage point.", "bbox": [81.4, 1470.1, 554.2, 1495.0]}]}